trans-unit.source: Combines multiple dependencies between an item stored in an ASP.NET application's <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"></xref> object and an array of <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kombinerer flere avhengigheter mellom et element som er lagret i en ASP.NET-programmet <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"> </xref> objekt og en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The AggregateCacheDependency class monitors a collection of dependency objects so that when any of them change, the cached item is automatically removed.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AggregateCacheDependency overvåker en samling avhengighet objekter slik at når en av dem endrer bufrede elementet fjernes automatisk.

trans-unit.source: The objects in the array can be <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> objects, <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> objects, custom objects derived from <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>, or any combination of these.
trans-unit.target: Objekter i matrisen kan være <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>objekter, <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>objekter, egendefinerte objekter som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>, eller en kombinasjon av disse.</xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> </xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> </xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: The AggregateCacheDependency class differs from the <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> class in that it allows you to associate multiple dependencies of different types with a single cached item.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AggregateCacheDependency er forskjellig fra det <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>klasse ved at den gjør det mulig å knytte flere avhengigheter av forskjellige typer med ett element for bufrede.</xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you create a page that imports data from a SQL Server database table and an XML file, you can create a <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency> object to represent a dependency on the database table and a <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> to represent the dependency on the XML file.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du oppretter en side som importerer data fra en SQL Server-databasetabellen og en XML-fil, kan du opprette en <xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>objektet som representerer en avhengighet i databasetabellen og en <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>til å representere avhengigheten av XML-filen.</xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> </xref:System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: Rather than making an <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method call for each dependency, you can create an instance of the AggregateCacheDependency class with each dependency added to it.
trans-unit.target: I stedet for å få en <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metodekall for hver avhengighet, kan du opprette en forekomst av klassen AggregateCacheDependency med hver avhengighet legges til den.</xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can then use a single <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A> call to make the page dependent on the AggregateCacheDependency instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan deretter bruke én <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A>samt siden avhengige AggregateCacheDependency-forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This is the default constructor for the <xref:System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency> class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er standardkonstruktør for <xref:System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency>klassen.</xref:System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"></xref> objects to the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"> </xref> objekter til den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The array of <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"></xref> objects to add.
trans-unit.target: En rekke <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"> </xref> objekter for å legge til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"></xref> object is referenced from more than one <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"></xref> entry.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency"> </xref> objektet refereres fra mer enn én <xref href="System.Web.Caching.Cache"> </xref> oppføring.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Henter filen avhengigheter.

trans-unit.source: The file dependencies.
trans-unit.target: Filavhengigheter.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a unique identifier for the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en unik identifikator for den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This method assigns a unique identifier to each dependency in the array and returns each of them.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden tilordner en unik identifikator til hver avhengighet i matrisen og returnerer dem.

trans-unit.source: The identifier is a combination of either the file name (for a file dependency) or the key name (for a cache-key dependency) and a string that this method assigns to the dependency.
trans-unit.target: IDen er en kombinasjon av filnavnet (for en fil avhengighet) eller Nøkkelnavn (for en Hurtigbuffernøkkel avhengighet) og en streng som denne metoden tilordner til avhengigheten.

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren for den <xref href="System.Web.Caching.AggregateCacheDependency"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: If one of the associated dependency objects does not have a unique identifier, the GetUniqueID method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en av de tilknyttede avhengighet objektene ikke har en unik identifikator, GetUniqueID returneres <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
